short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension optimizes daily work when adding freight - it automatically sends orders for cargo transportation.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension is intended for transport and forwarding companies for convenient work on cargo exchanges cargo.pl and trans.eu. The extension allows you to simultaneously add your cargo offers to two sites at once. To work with the extension, you must be registered on the indicated sites.

**Added work with transport offers.
*** Fixed minor bugs.
****Accelerated and improved freights
and bugs fixed.
